    "**Key differences:**\n",
    "\n",
    "| | REST | GraphQL |\n",
    "|--|------|---------|\n",
    "| Endpoint | One per resource (`/releases`, `/issues`, ...) | Single endpoint (`/graphql`) |\n",
    "| HTTP verb | `GET` for reading | `POST` (always) |\n",
