   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "o16kb5zic88",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "> **Troubleshooting — if `find_all()` returns an empty list:**\n",
    ">\n",
    "> | Problem | Fix |\n",
    "> |---------|-----|\n",
    "> | Wrong class name | Right-click → Inspect Element in your browser and double-check the exact class string — class names are case-sensitive |\n",
    "> | Page didn't load | Check `r.status_code` is `200`. If not, the site may be down or blocking you |\n",
    "> | Site structure changed | Websites change their HTML without warning. Re-inspect the page to find the new class names |\n",
    ">\n",
    "> **Quick debug:** Print `r.text[:500]` to see the first 500 characters of the HTML. If you see `<html>` and `<body>` tags, the page loaded correctly. If you see an error message, the request failed."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
